parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt buckle can cause the seat belt to malfunction, leading to a increased risk of injury or fatality in the event of an accident.
symptoms: the seat belt will not hold together
the seat belt fails to restrain
the seat belt buckle will not release.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Delayed or Unavailable Repair Parts for Seat Belt Buckle Recall
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay or unavailability of repair parts for the seat belt buckle recall can cause drivers to continue using faulty seat belts, increasing the risk of injury or fatality in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Dealers do not have parts in stock
owners are told to wait for parts
owners are unable to schedule repairs due to parts unavailability.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden separation of the tire from the rim can cause loss of vehicle control, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The tire comes off the rim while driving
or crashing; the tire itself is not damaged
